name: Shell Flavex 595 D

localDocs.name: Flavex 595 D India EN 140006501563 EHS V1.0 19-APR-2021

marketing: Shell Flavex Oil 595 D is a high viscosity aromatic process oil made from a residual oil fraction. This oil type is also known as RAE (residual aromatic extract). It is a potential substitute for distillate aromatic extracts (DAE) used as extender oils in rubber and tyres. It fully meets the requirements of EU Tyre Directive 2005/69/EC.
